sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant LlamaService as Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant LlamaPod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Inference Provider<br/>(Ollama/vLLM/TGI)<br/>varies/TCP HTTP/gRPC
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>kubectl/ServiceAccount Auth
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources Created

    Note over Controller,LlamaPod: Flow 2: Health Check
    Controller->>LlamaService: GET /providers<br/>HTTP/8321 No Auth
    LlamaService->>LlamaPod: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaPod-->>LlamaService: Health Status
    LlamaService-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Status<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Provider: Flow 3: Inference Request
    User->>LlamaService: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTP/8321 No Auth
    LlamaService->>LlamaPod: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaPod->>Provider: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/gRPC No Auth
    Provider-->>LlamaPod: Prediction Result
    LlamaPod-->>LlamaService: JSON Response
    LlamaService-->>User: 200 OK

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 Bearer Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>TLS (insecureSkipVerify)
